Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.02,0:00:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个也不行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.51,0:00:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能买个新的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.51,0:00:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修一下还能用一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是说新的就一定好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在大学那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样…没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有按时出席吗  学分有拿到么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好  藤本一直都在打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.47,0:00:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠又跌倒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满身是泥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:01:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在什么都没有的地方也会跌倒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
